<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Aeroflow</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #8a2be2; /* Violet */
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f0e6ff; /* Light violet */
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #8a2be2;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Aeroflow!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for signing up for <strong>Aeroflow</strong>. Your account has been successfully created!</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p>Email: {{email}}</p>
                <p>Password: {{password}}</p>
                <p>Login here: <a href="{{siteUrl}}" target="_blank">{{siteUrl}}</a></p>
            </div>

            <p>We recommend changing your password after your first login to keep your account secure.</p>

            <a href="{{siteUrl}}" class="btn">Go to Aeroflow</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{year}} Aeroflow. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>